{"tid":1851152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特區政府做到嘢!】警助逾百四鄂客離境","createTime":"2020-01-30T02:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T02:36:55.000Z","uid":297241,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"89ab6e59489a5292bd8e8ef83cd80722c9d99302","tid":1851152,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:21:00.000Z","msg":"【#武漢肺炎】警助逾百四鄂客離境<br />\n<br />\n因應新型冠狀病毒疫情最新情況，特區政府今（27）日<span style=\"color: red;\">全面調查所有在澳門的湖北省人士</span>，治安警察局今日上午9時<span style=\"color: red;\">派出200名警力</span>，合共巡查全澳86間酒店、公寓及賓館。截至下午2時，<span style=\"color: red;\">行動中合共協助144人離境</span>，其中有77名男性（包括5名男童）、67名女性（包括6名女童)。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有4名人士，2名男性（包括1男童）、2名女性（包括1女童）願意配合安排，前往指定地點集中管理，入住黑沙青年旅舍。<br />\n<br />\n亦有大部分湖北省旅客已於較早前自行離開本澳。"},{"pid":"c0eff7d72093564deeffefaf2705ad8460a76302","tid":1851152,"uid":22590,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:23:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">本澳</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003504414d71d3949a51188d3901c3baeb626c14","tid":1851152,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"香港歸埋澳門算"},{"pid":"ff40a2a6da0c7d20d713a1bd9152bebdd19dea24","tid":1851152,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:29:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻暴政</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d90f3a685f1c209c77e9823a5ab3a699b1a8e38e","tid":1851152,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港歸埋澳門算</blockquote><br />\nYou earned 0.1 yen on this post,<br />\nbut since you have already earned 0.3 yen within today,<br />\nyou will not get any reward."},{"pid":"2e431afd8d10663a1e1e2afbe7ee8eeaafbc9e9b","tid":1851152,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:33:26.000Z","msg":"慘過返澳門"},{